      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## 🎉 Highlights\n\n### ✍️ Text Saving\n\nThe input modal now supports two independent pipelines:\n\n- **Save Text** — Paste any text directly as a Markdown note, no URL required\n- **Save Webpage** — Paste a URL to automatically download and convert the page to Markdown\n\nBoth functions share the same input box. Paste multiple lines at once — URLs are auto-detected per line.\n\n### 🚀 Quick Launch & Home Screen Shortcuts\n\nInstantly invoke Share to Save without opening Obsidian and clicking the ribbon:\n\n- **Android**: Create a home screen shortcut via Shortcut Maker — tap the icon to launch Obsidian and pop up the URL input modal\n- **iOS**: Add the `obsidian://share-to-save` URI Scheme to your Home Screen via the Shortcuts app\n- **Within Obsidian**: The URI `obsidian://share-to-save` can be called from any plugin or template\n\nStep-by-step setup guides are built into the settings tab — no external docs needed.\n\n### 🔧 Other Improvements\n\n- Manual clipboard button (clipboard-check icon at the bottom-right of the input), replacing auto-read for better privacy\n- Input UX improvements: auto-focus, Enter to submit, clipboard button fill\n- Fixed `openInputModal` race condition and missing error handling in `handleUrlInput`\n- Fixed Obsidian review warnings: `requestAnimationFrame` → `window.requestAnimationFrame` for popout window compatibility; async event callbacks → Promise chains\n\n---\n\n## 🎉 重点更新\n\n### ✍️ 文字保存功能\n\n输入框现在支持两条独立管线：\n\n- **保存文字** — 输入任意文本，直接保存为 Markdown 笔记，无需包含 URL\n- **保存网页** — 输入 URL，自动下载网页内容并转换为 Markdown\n\n两项功能共用一个输入框，一次可粘贴多行，逐行智能识别 URL。\n\n### 🚀 快速调用与桌面快捷方式\n\n现在可以一键唤起 Share to Save，无需手动打开 Obsidian 再点击 ribbon：\n\n- **Android**：使用 Shortcut Maker 创建桌面快捷方式，在桌面点击图标直接唤起 Obsidian 并弹出 URL 输入框\n- **iOS**：通过快捷指令 App，添加 `obsidian://share-to-save` URI Scheme 到主屏幕\n- **Obsidian 内**：URI `obsidian://share-to-save` 可在任何插件/模板中调用\n\n设置页内置了分步骤指引，无需查阅外部文档。\n\n### 🔧 其他改进\n\n- 输入框新增剪贴板手动读取按钮（右下角 clipboard-check 图标），取消自动读取避免隐私隐患\n- 输入体验优化：自动聚焦、回车提交、剪贴板按钮填充\n- 修复 `openInputModal` 竞态条件与 `handleUrlInput` 错误处理缺漏\n- 修复 Obsidian 官方审核警告：`requestAnimationFrame` 改为 `window.requestAnimationFrame`（popout 窗口兼容）、async 事件回调改为 Promise 链式调用\n\n---\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/chenxiccc/Obsidian-Share-to-Save/compare/v4.2.0...5.0.0",
