      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/chenxiccc/Obsidian-Share-to-Save/compare/3.4.2...4.0.0\n\n---\n\n## iOS New Share Sheet Menu Support\n\niOS Obsidian 1.13.0 introduced a new native share sheet menu. The plugin no longer requires mobile installation on iOS ≥ 1.13.0.\n\n**What's new:**\n- Support for iOS Obsidian 1.13.0+ new share sheet menu — select `Share-to-Save` as the target folder when sharing, and the desktop plugin will automatically detect and process the shared content\n- Share menu `.md` files are auto-converted to standard queue entries on desktop via frontmatter `sts_id` detection\n- Uses `MetadataCache` for zero-I/O skip of already-processed files\n- No mobile plugin installation required for iOS ≥ 1.13.0\n\n**See [README](https://github.com/chenxiccc/Obsidian-Share-to-Save#installation) for installation guide.**\n\n---\n\n## 支持 iOS 新分享菜单\n\niOS Obsidian 1.13.0 引入了新的原生分享菜单。iOS ≥ 1.13.0 时手机无需安装插件。\n\n**更新内容：**\n- 支持 iOS Obsidian 1.13.0+ 新分享菜单 — 分享时选择 `Share-to-Save` 为目标目录，桌面端插件自动检测并处理\n- 分享菜单生成的 `.md` 文件在桌面端自动转换为标准队列条目（通过 frontmatter `sts_id` 检测）\n- 通过 `MetadataCache` 零 I/O 跳过已处理文件\n- iOS ≥ 1.13.0 时手机无需安装插件\n\n**详见 [README](https://github.com/chenxiccc/Obsidian-Share-to-Save#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E)。**",
